msgid "Afterward, simply run your file:"
msgstr "Afterward, simply run your file:"

#: ../../source/graphql/quick-start.rst:196
msgid ""
"info **Hint** You can also compile a script beforehand and use ``node`` "
"executable instead."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/graphql/quick-start.rst:199
msgid ""
"In order to switch to the watch mode (automatically generate typings on "
"any ``.graphql`` file change), pass ``watch`` option to the "
"``generate()`` method."
msgstr ""

